<http://model.geneontology.org/ev_w_id_REACTO_R-HSA-9907947_R-HSA-9908171_R-HSA-9958874_component_BFO_0000051_UniProtKB_P35998_R-HSA-9907947_R-HSA-9958874_component_Reactome_R-HSA-9958825>
